{"type":"message","id":"2f6735c2","parentId":"35adee36","timestamp":"2026-03-11T10:59:45.123Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-03-11 18:59 GMT+8] please meticulously review /home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/skills/trustskill/SKILL.md which you are supposed to use to scan any new skill downloaded and before adding any new skill to your skills inventory. remember this and record it \n in your long term record memory."}],"timestamp":1773226785118}}
